<i>as a two-family house</i>

775
00:41:08,766 --> 00:41:10,063
<i>with a porch and a fence</i>

776
00:41:10,134 --> 00:41:14,468
<i>You won't believe what you see</i>
<i>when you look at her</i>

777
00:41:15,506 --> 00:41:17,974
<i>She's enormous colossal</i>
<i>tremendous gigantic immense</i>

778
00:41:19,510 --> 00:41:21,273
