<i>And we need the rent</i>

800
00:42:33,083 --> 00:42:35,950
<i>That'll be a cinch</i>
<i>Cuz when we're in a pinch</i>

801
00:42:36,020 --> 00:42:39,319
<i>l can put her to work</i>
<i>under a circus tent</i>

802
